**Inspecting target id details**

I’m looking into something involving target-art116 and its operations, specifically checking the seed and recipe requirements. It seems I need to figure out if envctl_migration_runs has a foreign key to the envctl_migration_targets' id. I should inspect the schema columns to verify if a target id foreign key is necessary. There’s a bit to unpack here, so I want to be thorough!
